NG0411:1: @#// bcom ldan 'das mya ngan med pa'i dpal la phyag 'tshal lo //
NG0411:2: gzhi rtsa med pa'i chos nyid byang chub sems //
NG0411:3: zab cing phra bas dpag pa'i yul las 'das //
NG0411:4: yangs shing khyab pas nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam //
NG0411:5: sbom zhing rags pas snang srid dbang du bsdus //
NG0411:6: de 'dra'i chos sku bla med byang chub sems //
NG0411:7: ma byung ma skyes 'od kyi snying po can //
NG0411:8: 'gro ba yongs kyi dpal mgon byang chub sems //
NG0411:9: sgra dang tha snyad tshig gi spyod yul med //
NG0411:10: dpag med bsam 'das mi gnas mya ngan 'das //
NG0411:11: don gyi snying po bla med byang chub sems //
NG0411:12: smra bsam brjod med rig pas pha rol phyir //
NG0411:13: mi skye mi 'gag rang rig byang chub sems //
NG0411:14: mi gnas bdag med ye nas rnam par dag /
NG0411:15: ma bcos lhun grub bde chen snying po mchog /
NG0411:16: sbyir yang snang ba bde chen longs spyod sku //
NG0411:17: rang byung ye shes sprul sku byang chub sems //
NG0411:18: bdag med spros bral don dam lhun gyis rdzogs //
NG0411:19: nyag gcig ma 'gags snying po byang chub sems //
NG0411:20: ma skyes dbyings nas rang byung kun la khyab //
NG0411:21: mkha' ltar dngos med zhi ba gcig tu grags //
NG0411:22: nyi ma'i snying po dngos med mya ngan 'das //
NG0411:23: rang byung 'gag med skar tshogs grangs mang yang *//
NG0411:24: bdag nyid chen po mi 'gyur bdag nyid sku //
NG0411:25: thugs rje thabs mkhas nas mkha'i sprin gyi tshul //
NG0411:26: phan gnod yod med snying po byang chub la //
NG0411:27: las dang thugs rje nam mkha'i sprin gyi tshul //
NG0411:28: zhe gtsang med pa chos nyid byang chub sems //
NG0411:29: rig pa'i rtsal chen ma 'gags rang rig yongs la khyab //
NG0411:30: rdo rje sems dpa'i thugs rje 'od po che //
NG0411:31: nyi ma thog tu chu sprin ga bur bzhin //
NG0411:32: rdo rje sems dpa'i zhal chems nyag gcig ma //
NG0411:33: dga' rab rdo rje mkhas pa'i skye mchog gis //
NG0411:34: las 'phro skal bar ldan pa'i thugs brgyud nas //
NG0411:35: bsnan phri med pa'i rin chen gter 'di chongs //
NG0411:36: snod ngan bu dang rgyud ngan slob ma la //
NG0411:37: chu srin gre ba bzhin du dam du sdoms //
NG0411:39: de nas byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen pos /
NG0411:40: rgyud dag pa'i rdo rje sems dpa' la zhu ba drug zhus pa /
NG0411:41: kye thugs rje chen po khams gsum gyi sems can thams cad ni nad pa lta bu'o //
NG0411:48: rdo rje 'dzin pa nyon cig / ngas sdaum pa tshig gsum nges bstan gyis //
NG0411:49: legs par yid la zungs shig / 'khor ba'i rgya
NG0411:50: mtsho thag rings rnam par dag pa'i zhing du bsgral
NG0411:51: ba dang */ 'khor ba'i 'dam rdzab la rdo rje rdzong bca' ba dang */
NG0411:52: sdug bsngal gyi bye brag nor bu rin po cher sgyur ba dang gsum la /
NG0411:53: rigs kyi bu phyi snod kyi 'jig rten thams cad 'byung ba lngas bsdus pa /
NG0411:54: sngon byung gi dus na sangs rgyas kyi zhing yongs su dag pa /
NG0411:59: rgya yongs su ma chad pa /
NG0411:60: tshig dang dbang po'i sbyod yul med pa /
NG0411:61: brjod bya thams cad las 'das pa /
NG0411:62: 'das zhes bya ba yang ming gi rnam grangs te /
NG0411:63: ming tsam la yang mi gnas pa'o //
NG0411:64: des ni 'khor ba rgya mtsho mtha' rings ba rnam par dag pa'i zhing du bsgral ba'o //
NG0411:65: khams gsum sems can sdug bsngal gyi grur tshud /
NG0411:66: ma rig pa'i rgyar 'thums nas sdug bsngal bar gnas kyang */
NG0411:67: snying po byang chub kyi sems rang byung rang 'od gsal ba'i /
NG0411:68: rgyu rkyen med par ka dag pas /
NG0411:69: rdo rje lta bu'i ye shes la gnas su rung
NG0411:70: gi / gdos pa can shes rab kyi snying po
NG0411:71: med pa ni ma yin no //
NG0411:72: rgyud drug gi sems can thams cad rdo rje snying
NG0411:73: po'i sku dri ma med par gnas pas yongs la
NG0411:74: khyab / gzhan dbang du gyur pa /
NG0411:75: zad cing dri bas rgya ma chad /
NG0411:76: thabs kyi rgyal po stobs kyi rig pa shar bas /
NG0411:77: 'khor ba nyid rang byung gi ye shes su ka
NG0411:78: dag / sdug bsngal gyi 'dam rdzab nyid bde ba
NG0411:80: 'khor ba'i 'dam rdzab la rdo rje'i rdzong bcas pa'o //
NG0411:81: rigs kyi bu nyon cig / sems can thams cad la lus gsum du shes pa'o //
NG0411:82: ye shes kyi lus sdug bsngal gyi mtha' las grol ba'o //
NG0411:83: bag chags smin pa'i lus sha khrag gi gdos pa can /
NG0411:84: gnyis 'brel gyi lus sems bde sdug gnyis 'dzin /
NG0411:85: gzhi shes pa chos kyi sku la /
NG0411:86: bag chags kyi nad med kyang */
NG0411:87: rnam rtog sems kyi lus bag chags nad du langs pas /
NG0411:88: gso byed sman pa'i rgyal pos gso byed sman gyis gso zhes 'byung ste /
NG0411:90: rig pa mya ngan 'das pas gso /
NG0411:91: sdug bsngal 'dam rdzab lta bu'i nad /
NG0411:92: bde ba chen po zag pa med pa'i ye shes kyis gso /
NG0411:93: gti mug mun pa lta bu'i nad /
NG0411:94: shes rab mar me rlung gi ma bskyod pa lta bus gso /
NG0411:95: bag chags sbyar rtsi lta bu'i nad /
NG0411:96: rang bzhin med pa man shel lta bus gso /
NG0411:97: rtog pa'i rtsing zhib zug rngu tsher ma lta bu'i nad /
NG0411:98: mnyam pa nyid mi g.yo ba rgya mtsho lta bu'i sman gyis gso /
NG0411:99: de ni sdug bsngal gyi bye brag rin po cher bsgyur ba zhes bya'o //
NG0411:100: zhes byang chub kyi sems rma bya mjing bsnol gyi rgyud dag las /
NG0411:101: gzhi chos kyi sku'i rang bzhin bstan pa'i le'u ste dang po'o ///
NG0411:102: / de nas byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen pos yang zhusapa /
NG0411:103: kye ma bcom ldan rdo rje 'chang *//
NG0411:104: zag med lam la rab gnas pa'i //
NG0411:105: de bzhin gshegs pa'i bsam gtan gyis //
NG0411:106: blo dngos gnyis med sbyor ba ni //
NG0411:107: sangs rgyas nyid kyi dgongs pa ste //
NG0411:108: thabs la mkhas pas bstan du gsol //
NG0411:110: rdo rje 'dzin pa khyod nyon cig / dri ba dris pa de legs so //
NG0411:111: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dgongs pa dpag tu med kyang */
NG0411:112: sems can gyi blo'i bye brag dang sbyar nas /
NG0411:114: bzhin ma la blo de bzhin ma gnas pa'i ched du /
NG0411:115: mar me'i sdong bu bsnan pa'i tshul du /
NG0411:116: ma bcos ji bzhin gnas na de bzhin nyag gcig ces bya'o //
NG0411:118: bstan bya ston byed gnyis yod na //
NG0411:119: bsgom bya sgom byed ci phyir min //
NG0411:121: byang chub kyi snying po la /
NG0411:122: byang chub kyi snying po bstan te */
NG0411:123: snying po bstan par bya ba'i don du /
NG0411:124: dus rtag tu snying po la gnas par bya'o //
NG0411:125: rtogs pa'i don shes bya ba ma 'gags kyang */
NG0411:126: bka' lung gi phyi mor rang rgyud la mi gsal gyi bar du /
NG0411:127: shes bya la gsal gdab cing ting nge 'dzin la gnas par bya'o //
NG0411:128: byang chub snying po 'gyur med chos kyi sku //
NG0411:129: gzhan nas ma btsal sems nyid mngon sangs rgyas //
NG0411:130: rang la gnas pa'i don de sems kyi sems la ltos //
NG0411:131: ma byung ma skyes rang byung chos kyi sku //
NG0411:132: mi g.yo mi 'gyur mnyam pa chen por zhog / gsal la rtog med mi 'gyur chos kyi sku //
NG0411:133: ma bcos bde ba chen po'i ngang du gzhag / sku gsum lhun grub bkod pa rgyan gyi sku //
NG0411:134: bde chen 'du 'bral med pa'i ngang la gzhag / thig le nyag gcig rang bzhin spros dang bral //
NG0411:135: sna tshogs shar kyang nyag gcig nyid du bsgom //
NG0411:136: nam mkha'i mthong nas gsal ba'i nyi shar bzhin //
NG0411:137: skye med dbyings nas rang byung 'od gsal ba //
NG0411:138: thugs rje sprul pa'i 'od zer 'phro bar bsgom //
NG0411:139: snang srid rnam par dag pa pad+mo'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NG0411:140: bskyed rdzogs rnam gsum ma btsal lhun gyis rdzogs //
NG0411:141: bsod nams ye shes tshogs chen dag pa'i sku //
NG0411:142: kun tu bzang po'i mdzad spyod rtogs pa'i sgom //
NG0411:143: sgrib gnyis ma sbyangs tshogs gnyis lhun gyis rdzogs //
NG0411:144: man shel lta bur dri med gdod nas dag / rnam rtog skyon bral ye shes lhun gyis grub //
NG0411:145: rang byung rdo rje snying po yin par bsgom //
NG0411:146: ma bcos chos sku kun gzhi byang chub sems //
NG0411:147: sa la ma bgrod lam la mi gnas kyang *//
NG0411:148: rtog pa gdeng du ma gyur bar du bsgom //
NG0411:149: sangs rgyas nyag gcig chos la mi gnas kyang *//
NG0411:150: 'khrul rtog spang phyir chos nyid ngang du bsgom //
NG0411:151: dug snga ye shes lnga ru sangs rgyas kyang *//
NG0411:152: rnam grol zag med lnga ru gsal bar bsgom //
NG0411:153: 'byungs lnga lha mo lnga ru sangs rgyas kyang *//
NG0411:154: mdzes pa'i lha mo sprul sku gsal bar bsgom //
NG0411:155: snang srid rnam dag brjod pa las 'das kyang *//
NG0411:156: zhing khams rnam dag chos sku'i ngang du bsgom //
NG0411:157: byang chub sems dpa' skye shi mi mnga' yang *//
NG0411:158: 'du 'bral med pa rgyun gyi theg pa bsgom //
NG0411:159: 'dod do snod bcud dngos po rnam dag kyang *//
NG0411:160: ci la ma chags mi rtog ting 'dzin bsgom //
NG0411:161: 'khor dang longs spyod skar tshogs brgyan mang yang *//
NG0411:162: ci la ma chags rang bzhin rnam dag bsgom //
NG0411:163: sgyu ma'i phung po'i ye shes gnas yin kyang *//
NG0411:164: ma chags mi gnas btang snyoms chen por bsgom //
NG0411:165: kun gzhi rnam she sku la @#//
NG0411:167: rang byung ye shes bdag med mya ngan 'das //
NG0411:168: rtag chad tshig las 'das par sun phyung nas //
NG0411:169: mthon dman glong du khod snyoms te //
NG0411:170: mnyam pa chen po mnyam las 'das par bsgom //
NG0411:171: brjos pa'i tha snyad tshig las 'das par rab rtogs na //
NG0411:172: rnam dag byang chub dbyings kyi bsgom pa yin //
NG0411:173: ces byang chub kyi sems rma bya mjing bsnol gyi rgyud las /
NG0411:174: gzhi lam dang bcas pa'i le'u ste gnyis pa'o ///
NG0411:175: / de nas byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen pos zhus pa /
NG0411:176: ston pa thugs rje mnga' bas /
NG0411:177: 'gro ba'i mgon po bde bar gshegs //
NG0411:178: gzhi lam 'bras bu gnyis med pa'i //
NG0411:179: lam gyi 'bras bu bshad du gsol //
NG0411:181: rigs kyi bu nyon cig / dri ba dris pa de legs so //
NG0411:182: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas kyi gdams pa rin po che ni /
NG0411:183: brjod pa thog tu+u mi phebs shing bstan par dka' na yang */
NG0411:184: ngas re zhig mtshon pa'i tshig 'ga' tsam smra yis /
NG0411:185: sems la dbang thob gang zhe na /
NG0411:187: legs par yid la zung zhig / rigs kyi bu
NG0411:188: 'bras bu bla na med pa gud nas mi 'byung
NG0411:189: ngo // gzhi lam gnyis su med pa'i dus na /
NG0411:190: de bzhin gshegs pa'i bsam gtan zhes bya ste /
NG0411:191: lhag mthong dang zhi gnas gnyis su med nas rang
NG0411:192: byung gi ye shes mar me rlung gis mi bskyod
NG0411:193: pa lta bur / shes bya nyams su myong na /
NG0411:195: sangs rgyas nyag gcig ma zhes bya ste /
NG0411:196: ye shes dbyings nas gsal na 'bras bu nyag gcig ma //
NG0411:197: dbyings nyid rig par shar na 'bras bu nyag gcig ma //
NG0411:198: gzugs sku 'od du shar na 'bras bu nyag gcig ma //
NG0411:199: bde chen zag pa med na 'bras bu nyag gcig ma //
NG0411:200: snang srid dbang du bsdus na 'bras bu nyag gcig ma //
NG0411:201: ting 'dzin ro la ma chags 'bras bu nyag gcig ma //
NG0411:202: 'khor ba rang bzhin med na 'bras bu nyag gcig ma //
NG0411:203: mtshan ma zil gyis non na 'bras bu bde ba che //
NG0411:205: rgyu chos kyi sku la 'bras bu gzugs sku gnyis 'byung ba yang */
NG0411:206: thig le'i rtsal la ma 'gags pa yin te /
NG0411:207: de yang rgyu 'bras dbyer med pa nyid rtsal du shes pa'i dus su /
NG0411:208: 'bras bu sku gsung thugs mthar phyin pa'i /
NG0411:209: sku gsum ye shes rang byung du shar nas /
NG0411:210: ye shes gzugs skur snang la /
NG0411:211: gzugs nyid rang bzhin rnam par dag ste /
NG0411:212: mtshan ma las 'das na 'bras bu ye shes su grub bo //
NG0411:213: ngo bo nyid kyi snang ba snang tshod du grags tshod me long g.ya' dag pa ltar bstan kyang */
NG0411:214: don dam pa spros pa dang bral ba rang bzhin rnam par dag pa /
NG0411:215: 'bras bu mi gnas pa'i ye shes chen po zhes bya'o //
NG0411:216: mtshan ma dang bral ba tshan kyi sku /
NG0411:217: bya ba thams cad dang bral ba 'bras bu bla na med pa zhes bya'o //
NG0411:218: phyir mi ldog pa'i lung nges pa bka' lung gi phyi mo @#//
NG0411:220: ye ji bzhin pa'i rdo rje 'chang chen po /
NG0411:221: rgyud dag pa'i rdo rje 'chang la snang ba'i dus na /
NG0411:222: rgyu 'bras dbyer mi phyed ba'i rang byung gi bcom ldan 'das zhes bya ste /
NG0411:223: rgyud dag pa'i dbyings nyid nas /
NG0411:224: 'bras bu ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor rang snang gi dus na /
NG0411:225: rgyu 'bras kyi chos thams cad mi phyed pas /
NG0411:226: sangs rgyas mar me mdzad stong gi gtsug phud rin po che zhes bya bar grags te /
NG0411:228: rang gi shes bya mthar phyin pa'i dus na /
NG0411:229: bdud dang mu stegs kyi glags mi rnyed la /
NG0411:230: phya dang dbang phyug gi grogs byar med /
NG0411:231: rgyal mtshan gyi rtse mo ltar nub pa med cing */
NG0411:232: nor bu rin po che ltar zad mi shes la /
NG0411:233: shes bya rang gi ngo bo la shes bya rang gi dbang bskur ba'i dus na /
NG0411:234: 'phags pa gtsug tor dri ma med pa zhes grags so //
NG0411:235: byang chub kyi sems la byang chub kyi sems dus su /
NG0411:236: rgya mtsho chen por chu bran 'du ba'i tshul te /
NG0411:237: chos nyid skye ba med pa'i glong du chos can
NG0411:238: mtshan mar snang ba'i dus thams cad rang bzhin gyis
NG0411:240: byang chub sems dpa' kun tu bzang po zhes grags so //
NG0411:241: chos thams cad la dbye ba med cing bzang ngan du mi lta /
NG0411:242: bdag dang gzhan du mi rtogs pa'i dus na /
NG0411:243: nam mkha' dang nyi ma'i tshul te /
NG0411:244: byang chub sems dpa' byams pa kun nas gzigs zhes grags so //
NG0411:245: chos thams cad gang yang mi len /
NG0411:248: gang gis kyang sgrol mi nus /
NG0411:251: rang bzhin rnam par dag pas rtag pa'i mtha' med /
NG0411:252: shes bya ngo bo la ma bsgribs yongs su gsal bas /
NG0411:253: chad pa'i mtha' med pa / 'phags pa nam mkha'i snying po zhes grags so //
NG0411:254: zhes byang chub sems dpa' rma bya mjing bsnol gyi
NG0411:255: rgyud las / gzhi lam 'bras bu rnam pa gsum
NG0411:256: mthar phyin par bstan pa'i le'u ste gsum
NG0411:258: / de nas byang chub semasadapa' sems dpa' chen pos yang zhus pa /
NG0411:259: 'jam dpal gzhon nu dpa' bo mchog / gzhi lam 'bras bu mthar phyin pas //
NG0411:260: nyon mongs 'khor ba'i rgyun yang gcod //
NG0411:261: dag pa'i zhing du yang dag bsgral //
NG0411:262: rnam rtog zil gyis mnan phyir ro //
NG0411:263: spyod pa'i tshul khrims bshad du gsol //
NG0411:265: rdo rje sems dpa' 'ang bdag la nyon //
NG0411:266: spyod pa rnam pa gsum du rtag / glang po lam du zhugs pa'i spyod pa dang */
NG0411:267: smyon pa snying stor pa dran pa med pa'i spyod pa dang */
NG0411:270: bya thib tshang du zhugs pa dang */
NG0411:271: bu gcig pa'i ma lta bu ste /
NG0411:272: da ni rnal 'byor chen po'i spyod pa yin /
NG0411:273: dpa' brtul stag gi spyod pa dang */
NG0411:274: brtul zhugs phag gi spyod pa dang */
NG0411:275: sems med bung ba'i spyod pa dang */
NG0411:276: dbang sdud mu stegs kyi spyod pa dang */
NG0411:277: bde ba thun 'jug gi spyod pa dang */
NG0411:280: dman pa phyag dar khrod kyi spyod pa dang */
NG0411:281: mtshon pa nyams myong gi spyod pa dang */
NG0411:282: 'dod pa bya ba'i spyod pa dang */
NG0411:283: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
NG0411:284: lta ba glong du gyur pa'i spyod pa ni /
NG0411:286: zhes thugs kyi rgyud nas kyang bshad do //
NG0411:287: chos nyid glong du gyur pa'i spyod pa ni /
NG0411:288: ci la yang ma zhen ma chags pa'o //
NG0411:289: nyams myong rgyud la skyes pa'i spyod pa ni /
NG0411:291: brtul zhugs kyi spyod pa'i spyod pa ni /
NG0411:292: bya ri skegs lta bu ste ma nges pa'o zhes gsungs so //
NG0411:293: byang chub sems dpa'i spyod pa'i mtha' ni ma bcos pa'o //
NG0411:294: rang bzhin rnam par dag pa'i dus na /
NG0411:295: spyi la yang ma zhen pa'i spyod pa rnam par dag pa'o //
NG0411:296: bde ba chen po yul du shar ba'i dus su /
NG0411:297: zug rngu'i mtha' rang bzhin gyis 'gog / khyad par na rgyu+u la skyes pa'i dus na /
NG0411:298: snying rje chen po lhag par can gyi spyod pa skye bar 'gyur ro //
NG0411:299: 'dod pa med par 'gro ba rigs drug gi gnas yul du snang ba'i dus su /
NG0411:300: chos thams cad ci la yang ma chags pa'i spyod pa skye bar 'gyur ro //
NG0411:301: sangs rgyas kyi zhing yongs su dag pa la yul du snang ba'i dus su /
NG0411:302: thun mong gi dngos po 'gags nas ngo tsha ba dang bag tsha ba'i 'du shes med de /
NG0411:303: tshig nam mkha' la khungs ston to //
NG0411:304: spyan nam mkha' la gzigs te /
NG0411:305: mdzub mo nam mkha' la stod pa'i spyod pa 'char ro //
NG0411:306: chos kyi sku sprul pa'i nyams su btar ba'i dus su /
NG0411:307: lus grang dro dang na tsha med cing gcer bu'i spyod pa rang byung shar te /
NG0411:308: nam mkha'i ri mo khungs 'don pa'o //
NG0411:309: zag pa med pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis ro nyams su myong ba'i dus su /
NG0411:310: zas kyi 'du shes chung zhing grogs la mi chags par /
NG0411:311: ri dwags rma sam ltar gcig pu ri sul 'grim pa'i spyod pa 'char ro //
NG0411:312: sems ye shes kyi dbang du 'dus shing snang ba
NG0411:313: chos nyid kyi dbang du 'dus pa'i du 'dus pa'i
NG0411:314: dus na / nam mkha' la 'gro ba dang */
NG0411:315: chu+u la mi nub par 'gro ba dang */
NG0411:316: gzhan gyis mi snang ba'i rtsal la spyod par 'gyur ro //
NG0411:317: rig pa'i dbyings la shar ba'i dus su //
NG0411:318: yul gzhan dag gi snang ba 'char bar 'gyur ro //
NG0411:319: sems las su rung ba'i dus su /
NG0411:320: gzhan gyi sems shes shing dngos po thams cad las brdzun du smra bar 'gyur ro //
NG0411:321: chos nyid pa stong nyid las su rung ba'i dus na /
NG0411:323: mi ma yin pa'i sgra thams cad sel bar 'gyur ro //
NG0411:324: spyod pa rnam par dag pa de rnams ni /
NG0411:325: rgyud dag pa'i rdo rje sems dpa' snang ste /
NG0411:326: lus ma bor bar mngon par rdzogs par sangs rgyas so ///
NG0411:334: de nas byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen po dga' mgu yi rangs te /
NG0411:335: bcom ldan 'das la thal mo snying khar sbyar nas /
NG0411:338: kye kye legs so dpal ldan mgon po che //
NG0411:339: zhal nas byung na dga' ba de //
NG0411:340: zhal nas gsungs pa'i nga nyid don gyi mchog / bdag blo mun pa kha 'byed pas //
NG0411:341: snang gsal thugs rje 'od kyi me //
NG0411:342: sems can kun gyi skyabs mdzad pas //
NG0411:343: mgon po dri med ye shes sku //
NG0411:344: 'gro ba'i don du sku sprul nas //
NG0411:345: rang byung sangs rgyas rnam par gzigs //
NG0411:346: byams mgon thugs rjes skyabs mdzad pa //
NG0411:347: sangs rgyas log par dad sel la //
NG0411:348: gus pa'i tshul gyis skyabs su mchi //
NG0411:350: byang chub sems dpa' rma bya mjing bsnol gyi rgyud las /
NG0411:351: spyod pa rtog pa'i le'u ste bzhi pa'o ///
NG0411:352: / de nas byang chub sems dpa' sems dpa' chen pos yang dri ba dris pas /
NG0411:353: 'jam dpal gzhon nur gyur pa thugs rje can //
NG0411:354: zhu+u ba zhus pa legs gsung pa //
NG0411:355: 'gro mgon rdo rje sems dpas mdzad //
NG0411:356: sangs rgyas thugs kyi dpal be'u dang *//
NG0411:357: sangs rgyas dbu yi gtsug tor dang *//
NG0411:358: sangs rgyas zhal gyi ljags bzang nas //
NG0411:361: rdo rje 'dzin pa khyod nyon cig / khyod kyi dri ba dris pa de legs so //
NG0411:362: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad la /
NG0411:363: thugs rje 'byung ba ni brjod kyi mi lang */
NG0411:365: ngas ma 'ongs pa'i sems can la mdo tsam zhig bstan gyis /
NG0411:366: khyod nyon cig / thugs rje'i bye brag mang gis kyang rtsal ma 'gags pa yin te /
NG0411:367: dper na nam mkha' sprin dang char gyi tshul 'byung ste /
NG0411:368: thugs rin po che'i dpa' be'u'i nas /
NG0411:369: sangs rgyas byams pa mi nyams mgon po zhes bya ba byung nas /
NG0411:370: rang bzhin rnam par dag pa'i chos bstan to //
NG0411:371: dbu'i gtsug tor nas 'jam dpal dri med snying po zhes bya ba byung nas /
NG0411:372: sku gdung ring bsrel gyi chos bstan te /
NG0411:374: sangs rgyas bye ba rnam par gzigs zhes bya ba byung nas /
NG0411:375: rgyu 'bras kyi chos ma lus par bstan to //
NG0411:376: sangs rgyas stong gi yon tan ni //
NG0411:377: sangs rgyas gcig pu nyid la 'dus //
NG0411:378: gcig pu rab tu snang ba'i chos //
NG0411:379: 'gro ba kun la rang bzhin gnas //
NG0411:381: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas thams cad kyi
NG0411:382: yon tan bsam gyis mi khyab pa gcig byung ste
NG0411:383: / de dag kyang sangs rgyas 'od dpag med chen po rtsal snang ngo *//
NG0411:384: sangs rgyas 'od dpag med nyid 'gro ba yongs kyi snying por shar nas //
NG0411:385: 'gro ba sems can thams cad la //
NG0411:386: snying po rnam dag ye shes rdzogs //
NG0411:388: sangs rgyas kun gyi gtsug phud lnga //
NG0411:389: rgyal mtshan rtse mo bzhin du gnas //
NG0411:390: sangs rgyas kun gyi che ba lnga //
NG0411:391: nam mkha' bzhin du khyab par gnas //
NG0411:392: rdo rje snying po bla na med //
NG0411:393: rin chen gtsug phud dri ma med //
NG0411:394: nges pa'i skyon rtog sel bar byed //
NG0411:397: mtha' la mi gnas phyag rgya che //
NG0411:398: mgon po dri ma med pa'i sku //
NG0411:399: yon tan kun gyi snying po shar //
NG0411:400: thabs mkhas thugs rje stobs kyi bdag / bdud bzhi
NG0411:401: 'dul mdzad dpa' bo mchog / dag pa'i zhing du
NG0411:402: yang dag sgrol // thugs rje'i chu bo rgyun mi 'chad //
NG0411:403: shes rab gru yis sgrol mdzad pa //
NG0411:404: sprin chen glog gi 'phreng ba can //
NG0411:405: rgyun gyi thugs rje'i rdo rje bdag / snying po bdag med ya ma brla //
NG0411:406: snying po rjes 'brangs spyod pa'i mtshon //
NG0411:407: nam mkha'i nyi mi'i tshul bzhin du //
NG0411:408: rang byung spros med mkha' la gdengs //
NG0411:409: rgyud dag pa yi dbyings nyid nas //
NG0411:410: 'bras bu ye shes dkyil 'khor rang snang ba'i dus su /
NG0411:411: snod bcud thams cad chos nyid du brdal ba //
NG0411:412: mi byed pa'i lta ba nam mkha' dang mnyam pas re dogs kyi 'phro gcad /
NG0411:413: zag pa med pa'i ye shes rang snang bas /
NG0411:414: bdag dang gzhan gyi don mthar phyin /
NG0411:415: shes rab kyi stobs ma 'gags pas /
NG0411:416: bdud dang srin po zil gyis mnan /
NG0411:417: kye rdo rje 'dzin pa nyon cig thabs la mkhas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' ni /
NG0411:418: sems can gyi pha ma yin gyis /
NG0411:419: de yang dri ma med pa'i don gyis gnas par bya'o //
NG0411:420: rtogs pa'i don la rtse gcig tu ma yengs par gnas pas /
NG0411:421: byang chub sems dpa'i bsam gtan zhes bya'o //
NG0411:422: 'jam dpal dri med snying po ngas /
NG0411:424: gsang ba'i rgyud gsum yang gsang thugs kyi rgyud //
NG0411:425: thugs nas phyung nas gdams par bzhag / sangs rgyas lag tu gtad pa'i phyir //
NG0411:426: sangs rgyas gtsug phud rnam par rgyal ba zhes bya ba /
NG0411:427: thugs las nor bu dri ma med pa'i rgyud mdzad do //
NG0411:428: 'bras bu bla na yod pa dang */
NG0411:429: bla na med pa'i theg pa shan dbye ba'i phyir /
NG0411:431: sangs rgyas bye ba rnam par gzigs zhes bya ba byung nas /
NG0411:432: byang chub kyi sems rma bya mjing bsnol mdzad do //
NG0411:433: sangs rgyas sprul pa'i sku ye shes kyi lus su gnas pa'i phyir /
NG0411:434: mdzod spu'i bu ga nas 'od zer lnga 'phros nas
NG0411:435: sangs rgyas bde ldan mgon po spyan ras gzigs zhes
NG0411:437: lha mo 'od zer gyi rgyud mdzad do //
NG0411:438: las dge sdig la mtho dman med par la bzla ba'i phyir /
NG0411:439: shangs kyi rlung sgrom nas mthu stobs kyi bdag po dpal phyag na rdo rje phyung ste /
NG0411:440: bya btsal med par ye shes bla ma'i rgyud phyung ste /
NG0411:441: chos las 'das pa'i sku yongs su rdzogs par bstan to //
NG0411:442: zhes byang chub sems rma bya mjing bsnol gyi rgyud /
NG0411:443: rdzogs pa chen po 'bras bu bla na med pa'i theg pa las le'u lnga pa'o ///
NG0411:444: / byang chub kyi sems rma bya mjing bsnol zhes bya ba'i rgyud /
NG0411:446: byang chub sems dpa' ro langs bde ba la gdams pa rdzogs so //  //
NG0411:447: byang chub kyi sems rma bya mjing bsnol bsgom na /
NG0411:448: ngan song gsum gyi gzhi gsog @#//
NG0411:449: go / byang chub kyi sems dkar dmar rnams gnyis rang rgyud du go na /
NG0411:450: sems can gyi gzugs su smin no //
NG0411:451: rgyud kyi rgyal po ting nge 'dzin mchog gi rgyud las /
NG0411:452: ta na dang ga na'i rtog pa bshad pa'i le'u ste bcu gcig pa'o ///
NG0411:453: / de skad ces yid byed pa po kun tu bzang pos /
NG0411:454: ci yang ma gsungs par bka' stsal pas /
NG0411:455: rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs pa rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas yab yum dang */
NG0411:456: zhi khro'i lha brgya rtsa brgyad kyi dkyil 'khor gyis /
NG0411:457: rgyud kyi rgyal po ting nge 'dzin mchog gi rgyud kyi don rtogs so //
NG0411:458: rgyud kyi rgyal po ting nge 'dzin mchog gi rgyud las /
